        330
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "Certificate profiles are <ph id=\"ph1\">[!INCLUDE[wit_nextref](../Token/wit_nextref_md.md)]</ph> policies that configure managed devices with the certificates they need so device users can connect to your on-premises company resources using connections like Wi-Fi or VPN.",
