    },
    {
      "content": "When you deploy certificate profiles, you provision devices with a trusted root certificate for your PKI, and configure them to request device specific certificates.",
      "pos": [
        583,
        748
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "You can create three types of certificate profiles:",
      "pos": [
        750,
        801
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "PKCS #12 (.PFX) Certificate Profile: this can be used with Android 4.0 or later, iOS 6.0 and later, and Windows 10 (desktop and mobile) and later.",
      "pos": [
        807,
        953
