    },
    {
      "content": "Help to keep company resources secure by using your enterprise public key infrastructure (PKI)",
      "pos": [
        1542,
        1636
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "Enable you to use server authentication for all connections like Wi-Fi and VPN because you have provisioned the required certificates on the managed devices",
      "pos": [
        1648,
        1804
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "Certificate profiles provide the following management capabilities:",
      "pos": [
